    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative FD3S RX-7, this example features the high-revving 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine with documented optimal compression across all chambers. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise five-speed manual gearbox and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional torque bias and corner-exit traction. The chassis maintains its original structural integrity, utilizing a lightweight double-wishbone suspension geometry that remains tight and responsive. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in its factory configuration, with particular attention paid to the intricate vacuum routing and thermal management systems. It is a mechanically pure, turn-key specimen for the serious collector seeking uncompromised performance and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
