    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-ready vehicle that has been meticulously curated since day one. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014free from even the smallest stone chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin retains its original integrity; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, the dashboard is pristine, and every electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of maintenance records included. Having lived its entire life in a climate-controlled garage and never seeing inclement weather, the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. From the untouched factory floor mats to the crystal-clear headlight lenses, every detail has been preserved to satisfy the most discerning enthusiast. This is, without exaggeration, the finest example of its kind currently on the market.",
